This documents containg main goals and reasons for apery-project accordign to the business.

The target audience of the apery-project could be small or medium size business which reqire CRM system posibilities.
System is based on the module architecture whick allow to create different configurations (module combinations) for
different business needs.

Main goals:

1. Opportunity to manage customers database in different context (ex. discont program).
2. Sales management posibilities.
3. Analize database information (grafics, diograms, reports).
4. Support different roles for users.